description.title: PSD to HTML
description: Converting your design to validated responsive HTML5 / CSS3 markup. Static pages or open source software such as WordPress or b2evolution. For other open source software please contact me.

bio:
Carolyn has over 10 years experience working with web technologies. She has strong development skills in PHP and MySQL and has also worked with responsive design with HTML5 and CSS3 for the past 5 years. She is experienced in converting web designs into validated codes, and customizing open source software as standalone website and integrating into existing system. She is comfortable working under Windows or Unix environment and is able to work independently and as part of a team. 
Carolyn has previously developed various Windows applications and system programs and scripts to streamline operation and document automation. She graduated from The University of Queensland with Bachelor of Science degree major in Computer Science.
Online portfolio: http://www.carolynluwong.com
